{"tid":1979492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲父母日日想洗我腦","createTime":"2020-04-19T12:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T15:06:32.000Z","uid":179319,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"657343d32abc3dbe43f6d81dd66eb4a2dc04b4ef","tid":1979492,"uid":179319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多個月之前已經明白左地平說，佢地講極都睇唔到個真相我都無謂繼續搞到家破人亡啦！<br />\n點知！近呢兩個月，唔知邊個send個肥仔傑嘅youtube片俾佢地，佢地日日聽日日播，好難頂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被逼之下，我都抱住和平持平心態入去嘗試睇，唉...前前後後不斷話暴力就係唔岩，啲comment仲要無咩邏輯，全部盲目支持。我好擔心，但係擔心又有咩用，佢地已經唔係藍咁簡單，完全係紅咁，我知道返唔到轉頭，佢地呢家仲想慫恿我投建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，為左屋企和平著想只能夠屋企忍，但係思想上不能忍！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033085c7e1890225acd088cf1f8030af1491fea1","tid":1979492,"uid":249794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:42:34.000Z","msg":"同佢地鬥紅啦 拿拿臨買返個毛主席像係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢地買百佳買外國貨就即刻屌7佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779804ce492ab693287657b602c8b964fb8b153e","tid":1979492,"uid":128616,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23a51a37884a9aba0ea30e05b10de914be4a6b5c","tid":1979492,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033085c7e1890225acd088cf1f8030af1491fea1","tid":